data.description: This wonderful home is back on the market due to previous buyer could not obtain financing.  Check out this great 4 bedroom 2 bathroom home with an open concept floor plan. Home features a kitchen with granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, a breakfast bar and over looked the dining and living room. Front room can be formal dining, living or can be left up to your imagination. The master bedroom features a large garden tub with a separate shower and large walk-in closet. The three spare bedrooms are oversized with good sized closets. Plenty of outside sitting space from the covered front port to the backyard sitting area.
